txt.en: 'The fell Wargs are everywhere I look, [placeholder]. The Rohirrim despise these deadly beasts, for they thirst for the blood of our horses and our men.\n\n'Will you hunt them with me, wanderer?'
Wargs can be found roaming the plains of the eastern Westfold.\n\nYou should defeat Wargs in the Westfold.
Hostile Wargs roam unchecked through the grasses of the Westfold.
Winmar can be found afield north of Grimslade.\n\nYou should speak with Winmar.
'You are the most efficient slayer of those beasts I have ever seen, [placeholder]. It was an honour to hunt with you!'
